1. This function returns a list of districts from the database.
2. It gets the logged-in user using JWT.
3. It applies pagination (page number and list size).
4. It sorts districts by name in ascending order.
5. It filters only active districts.
6. It supports search by district name.
7. It can filter only actual districts (non-police districts).
8. It can filter only police districts.
9. It fetches data using a dynamic Specification query.
10. If no data is found and user is DC, it returns that userâ€™s own district.
